{"tid":193694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"某親戚欠債,屋企比人電話騷擾,點做?","createTime":"2017-04-09T12:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:42:08.000Z","uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17f4a585585ac3d27c4aeb681e855d43aac0ae94","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"事緣係有位親戚借左錢走埋佬 之後我老豆近呢兩日不斷有留言話「再唔叫當事人出黎 我就會搞鳩你地」之類 條友知道我地地址同電話 <br />\n我地無同個親戚做過任何擔保既野 <br />\n<br />\n可以點做 家中兩老好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f07c4dafec2ff33cca146527912b7c720d2a2e","tid":193694,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"486cb1f45763cb072354ba82bb309accb0bcc8b8","tid":193694,"uid":2455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"b810f4a887aa38881e5d40dc1089335df71c7da5","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f5c189cc6d3e577b216892009b43783b0a4895","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"報警犬有人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0bf092bf12a4248bf0c16f2ec74766311514d4","tid":193694,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"下次打嚟錄音報警備案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己google方法"},{"pid":"73db20064ac6e8021e1c3c76a00d16a5c666bfd7","tid":193694,