":"2017-04-09T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗理，得個講字</blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n首先備案再打電話來同佢講報左荃警有乜事同差佬講佢每次打來直接收線過一排佢唔會打來"},{"pid":"4a1874fc3038504e3f2e9e5885bd9bec2a29a52b","tid":193694,"uid":2288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/inogWuMlqkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FinogWuMlqkU&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2b3b9154\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/inogWuMlqkU</a>"},{"pid":"98554a7a316d11a6b7a0c2d589ef668509ab29ca","tid":193694,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2abe14a90a07b502a31ed750a6b3f9f40036dca","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"個收數佬留左個電話比我地 我地應該打唔打比佢！"},{"pid":"41608c6ddca1eb737662a2c765ad8d66a184df57","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔洗理，得個講字</blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n首先備案再打電話來同佢講報左荃警有乜事同差佬講佢每次打來直接收線過一排佢唔會打來</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我地肯定無簽過任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b253790f99dad3321a9f6c0deb90534cac61aefd","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/inogWuMlqkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FinogWuMlqkU&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2b3b9154\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/inogWuMlqkU</a></blockquote><br />\n佢有我地屋企地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6973365231377563acafd15b5edf3b2d38e22a","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還錢</blockquote><br />\n都唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb4db3b6b527917d34135196f9b2b2fb04aa94d","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔關你事佢叫你搵人咪幫佢搵囉<br />\n<br />\n債仔真係唔值得可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘係個債主我地搵唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九成走去做擔保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa5d25f518434cf10f6e784ac84100f1a38d3df","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fff66f649f3fbd7b3607fbfa9c937c619da48d6","tid":193694,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9714b429aa4085a9c806ffd524180f4666afe12f","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>還錢</blockquote><br />\n都唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蘋果、東方報紙你唔去搵，民主黨、公民黨成班議員區議員你唔搵，上嚟連登，連登仔幫得你幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab4d8b85fc9239514aa03b490f0651073ab0b6d","tid":193694,"uid":47575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"老實<br />\n佢地得個講字<br />\n<br />\n淋紅油鎖大閘呢啲野已經唔會再發生<br />\n打電話/上門 就問佢幫邊間收數<br />\n听佢留個人資料, 再同佢講會報警備案<br />\n<br />\n通常咁樣佢地就會唔再上門<br />\n<br />\n總之佢講乜都唔駛理 佢地純粹靠嚇<br />\n一蚊都唔可以比佢 / 承諾佢幾時還<br />\n否則會瘋狂追<br />\n<br />\n可以直接話個親戚唔係度住的<br />\n上黎係無用, 我可以告你滋擾"},{"pid":"662df0f356926698c6e5adbef917232330c48d7d","tid":193694,"uid":2288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>還錢</blockquote><br />\n都唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蘋果、東方報紙你唔去搵，民主黨、公民黨成班議員區議員你唔搵，上嚟連登，連登仔幫得你幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔可以用強勁既鍵盤炮火幫佢係連登上火力鎮壓收數佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6ad0255c5276c14d7bae80de37dfa2d06dd5ad","tid":193694,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"借錢梗要還"},{"pid":"29d7ffa50f0b4e455294d7cdb7f241ad82f9aab9","tid":193694,"uid":66611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"我屋企都試過，之前有親戚攞咗我屋企地址去做擔保，攪咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上唔使理佢地，如果再打比你，只要話當事人唔係到同埋講已經報咗警。如果收到信就放落錯誤郵件，等郵差叔叔送返比送件人。<br />\n<br />\n如果如果去到最後頂唔順，就拔電話線。<br />\n<br />\n不過，你大廈保安盡唔盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果尻流就自己小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d08bb6104863b37d78daf8f2e7ca208f5d64db5","tid":193694,"uid":66611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都試過，之前有親戚攞咗我屋企地址去做擔保，攪咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上唔使理佢地，如果再打比你，只要話<span style=\"color: red;\">唔識當事人</span>同埋講已經報咗警。如果收到信就放落錯誤郵件，等郵差叔叔送返比送件人。<br />\n<br />\n如果如果去到最後頂唔順，就拔電話線。<br />\n<br />\n不過，你大廈保安盡唔盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果尻流就自己小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b848507849d2d5582f38b02fb2a1c059dd72c0c","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都試過，之前有親戚攞咗我屋企地址去做擔保，攪咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上唔使理佢地，如果再打比你，只要話當事人唔係到同埋講已經報咗警。如果收到信就放落錯誤郵件，等郵差叔叔送返比送件人。<br />\n<br />\n如果如果去到最後頂唔順，就拔電話線。<br />\n<br />\n不過，你大廈保安盡唔盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果尻流就自己小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時你同佢傾既時候係咪要鬥兇？"},{"pid":"745eb16cc1828ac3c4c67fa3a4ad6616b551f0a9","tid":193694,"uid":81852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3b251ed321f98e9abec89323ff30d05208dd0d1","tid":193694,"uid":82961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企都試過，之前有親戚攞咗我屋企地址去做擔保，攪咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上唔使理佢地，如果再打比你，只要話當事人唔係到同埋講已經報咗警。如果收到信就放落錯誤郵件，等郵差叔叔送返比送件人。<br />\n<br />\n如果如果去到最後頂唔順，就拔電話線。<br />\n<br />\n不過，你大廈保安盡唔盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果尻流就自己小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=