;&times;閣2&times;04室欠債還錢」，我舊屋係同座同層2&times;01室，嗰陣仲得16歲，成間屋仲要係得我一個，一睇到嗰下嚇到high high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明佢樓下d食蕉專業<br />\n<br />\n通常上唔到去，先用呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寄晒所有鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74674b1e91d4d3b0ab876422c6f8f329e27f346c","tid":193694,"uid":81852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f352164f5471a535d7d088e677305911b1fb057","tid":193694,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔關你事佢叫你搵人咪幫佢搵囉<br />\n<br />\n債仔真係唔值得可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘係個債主我地搵唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f19a608e6d3d397e206fc83d95a571c3efd7bf4","tid":193694,"uid":52611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n係，你自己睇下放債人條例，不過要睇下係咪比左收數公司跟又或者係財務公司收數，驚比你投訴仲驚過收唔翻筆數，所以凶下你地叫你地幫佢找架昨<br />\n<br />\n利申法律jj</blockquote><br />\n巴打同你講又唔理我，想人點幫你</blockquote><br />\nSor 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問俾左貴利收數會唔會係另一個玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我現階段洗唔洗打電話俾個收數佬先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要確定左係收數公司定財務公司先，問清楚佢，你上網搜尋放債人條例滋擾，有好多相關嘅條文可以俾你睇到，大鳩番佢轉頭</blockquote><br />\n謝謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以從咩方面知道佢係咪收數公司 <br />\n因為其實我地屋企知道既資訊好小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你直接打去問佢啦，多數都會答你，不過應該唔會開曬全名，唔答你既話咪唔好理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打"},{"pid":"bd9b3be5b8670402f21323c9ef6bbba64e769362","tid":193694,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"我屋企都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾個仆街親戚陷害 擅自填咗我父母名同屋企地址做擔保人<br />\n每個月都收到財務公司信件<br />\n間唔中有收數電話同粗口恐嚇短信<br />\n我父母起初都冇理到<br />\n<br />\n但之後d收數佬上門 係大廈走廊貼曬欠債大字報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又拍我地門<br />\n終於我忍唔住 影低咗d證據 同我爸媽去報警<br />\n事後冇人再找上門滋擾<br />\n但仲有寄信嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌已經持續咗成年半 總之有呢d咁嘅仆街親戚真係家門不幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過既然又唔係你爭人錢 你唔理唔幫手還 d財仔又奈你唔何嘅"},{"pid":"fd06a3cb7